          "SAMPLE": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": null,
              "free_text": [
                "Internal helium gas-jet target with 5 mm FWHM, and an",
                "average density of 7*10**12 particles/cm2."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "SISD",
                "SILI"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The detector array was installed in two",
                "internal pockets covering laboratory angular angle",
                "ranges of 27-37 deg and 74-88 deg. In front of each",
                "pocket, a double-sided silicon strip detector was",
                "installed with 285 um thickness and 64*64 mm2 active",
                "area. Inside the pocket at 80 degrees, there was a",
                "Si(Li) detector behind the silicon strip detector.",
                "The two detectors could be used as a dE-E telescope."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "METHOD": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "EDE",
                "INTB",
                "REC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " The Ni-58 beam was accelerated by the",
                "UNILAC-SIS18 accelerator complex, and injected into",
                "the Experimental Storage Ring (ERS) with an energy of",
                "150 MeV/u. The ERS was set to decelerate the",
                "stored ions to a final energy of 100 MeV/u,",
                "corresponding to a revolution frequency of 1.2 MHz.",
                "An electron cooler was used. The cooled Ni-58 beam",
                "interacted with a helium gas-jet. The low energy",
                "recoils were detected by an UHV compatible windowless",
                "detector system."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "ADD-RES": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "COMP"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Experimental results were compared to",
                "theoretical calculations"
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "THEO"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " Isoscalar giant monopole resonance",
                "contribution was determined from",
                "multipole-decomposition analysis."
              ]
            }
          ],
